title: Slaughter High-80`s
description:
Movie Description
Marty was the nerd everyone made fun of. Now it&#039;s five years later and he&#039;s throwing a reunion for all his old "friends" - does he have a surprise for them? Five years ago Marty got mad...Now he&#039;s going to get even.

Credits 
Cast: Caroline Munro 
Director: George Dugdale, Mark Ezra, Peter Litten 

Industry Reviews
"...Its grisly special effects are of the darkly comic, Grand Guignol variety....SLAUGHTER HIGH is effective schlock..."
Los Angeles Times - Kevin Thomas (05/12/1987)
